reviewText: If you enjoy hentai you'll find this dull.
I asked for Elfen Leid but I can't complain

When their villiage is destroyed and two elven sisters are captured by the enemy given it is a hentai movie i think we all know what comes next. It does have a good story however and the animation is very well-drawn
It was great. But to short. It look like they took it from other Anime.
I don't understand people I don't like it when the girl isn't happy it takes all the fun out of it for me honestly

This is typical Japanese anime fare. Way out there.. and fun to watch, because it's unique and different from any American offerings.
The DVD was crisp and clear and a pleasure..great fantasy entertainment.
